---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us — Frye's Printing" description="Learn about Frye's Printing, a family-owned commercial print shop serving Napa Valley with quality printing and personal service.">
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="bg-navy text-white py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-gold font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Our Story</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold">About Frye's Printing</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-6">Three Generations. One Standard.</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Frye's Printing is a third-generation, family-owned commercial print shop located in the heart of Napa Valley. For three generations, we've built our business on a simple principle: deliver exceptional print quality with the kind of personal service you only get from people who truly care.
            </p>
            <p>
              While the big print brokers send your work to anonymous facilities across the state, we produce the majority of work right here — under our roof, with our team, on our presses. That means you get direct access to the people making your project happen.
            </p>
            <p>
              We're proud to be part of the Napa community, serving local businesses, wineries, restaurants, and organizations with the same dedication we'd give our own family projects.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-warm-gray rounded-2xl aspect-[4/3] flex items-center justify-center">
          <p class="text-charcoal-light text-sm">Shop photo coming soon</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Napa Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-warm-gray">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-6">Why Napa Matters</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed text-lg">
          <p>
            When you need a press check for a critical print run, the last thing you want is a two-hour drive to Sacramento or San Francisco. At Frye's, your press checks happen right here in Napa — in wine country, not on the freeway.
          </p>
          <p>
            That convenience isn't just about saving time. It means you can be more involved in the process, catch issues early, and get exactly the result you're after. And if you need to stop by the shop to look at a proof or discuss a project? We're right around the corner.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-12 text-center">What We Stand For</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gold/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Quality First</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
            We never cut corners. Every job gets the attention it deserves, from file prep through final delivery.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gold/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Relationships Matter</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
            We build long-term partnerships with our customers. Your success is our success.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gold/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Community Committed</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
            We're invested in Napa Valley. We live here, work here, and are committed to supporting our local community.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

