        The people behind the presses — team photos coming soon.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        {[1, 2, 3].map(() => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
            <div class="aspect-square bg-warm-gray-dark flex items-center justify-center">
